{"type":"message","id":"dac7b0a1","parentId":"2aa75b58","timestamp":"2026-04-12T23:00:02.683Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:10a19bb7-7afb-4b24-8478-62555b540c2d daily-ping-telegram] Send daily ping to Telegram with this EXACT format:\n\n🌅 Daily Ping — {DAY}, {MMM} {DD}, {YYYY}\n\n💰 Bitcoin\n• Price: ${BTC_PRICE} USD\n• 24h: {BTC_CHANGE}% {TREND}\n\n📊 Tech Stocks\n• NVDA: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• MSFT: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• GOOGL: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• INTC: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• META: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n• AMD: ${PRICE} ({CHANGE}%) {TREND}\n\n📊 Market: S&P {SPX}, Nasdaq {NDX} — {BRIEF_COMMENTARY}\n\n🚀 Trending GitHub Repos (Created Since 2025)\n1. {repo} ⭐ {stars}K\n... (top 10)\n\n— ⏰ {HH}:{MM} SGT | Data: CoinGecko, Yahoo Finance, GitHub API\n\nFetch fresh data using:\n- Bitcoin: CoinGecko API (price + 24h change)\n- Stocks: Yahoo Finance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD)\n- Indices: S&P 500 and NasdaqComposite\n- GitHub: top 10 repos created since 2025, sorted by stars\n\nSend to Telegram target 1087368827 using the message tool.\nCurrent time: Monday, April 13th, 2026 - 7:00 AM (Asia/Singapore) / 2026-04-12 23:00 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776034802679}}
{"type":"message","id":"0de3db28","parentId":"dac7b0a1","timestamp":"2026-04-12T23:00:34.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user wants me to send a daily ping with financial and GitHub data to Telegram. Let me break down what I need to fetch:\n\n1. Bitcoin price and 24h change from CoinGecko\n2. Stock prices for NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD from Yahoo Finance\n3. S&P 500 and Nasdaq Composite indices\n4. Top 10 trending GitHub repos created since 2025, sorted by stars\n\nLet me start by fetching this data. I'll need to make API calls to get the current prices.\n\nLet me think about the best approach:\n- CoinGecko API for Bitcoin data\n- Yahoo Finance for stocks and indices\n- GitHub API for trending repos\n\nLet","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" I'll fetch the fresh data and send your daily ping. Let me gather the Bitcoin price, stock data, market indices"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:0","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd&include_24hr_change=true","extractMode":"text"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://query1.finance.yahoo.com/v8/finance/chart/NVDA,MSFT,GOOGL,INTC,META,AMD,^GSPC,^IXIC?interval=1d&range=2d","extractMode":"text"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.web_fetch:2","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://api.github.com/search/repositories?q=created:>2025-01-01&sort=stars&order=desc&per_page=10","extractMode":"text"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":17592,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17945,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776034802683,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a95ed17a1e3c431c"}}
