ate trading. Coinbase pays us for certain activity generated through this link. Prices displayed are informational.\\n Learn more\\n\\n Chart Range Bar\\n 1D 5D\\n\\n23.82%\\n\\n 1M\\n\\n33.35%\\n\\n 6M\\n\\n71.51%\\n\\n YTD\\n\\n69.05%\\n\\n 1Y\\n\\n213.78%\\n\\n 5Y\\n\\n-8.61%\\n\\n All\\n\\n19,063.13%\\n\\n Key Events\\n Mountain\\n\\n Advanced Chart\\n\\n Loading chart for INTC\\n\\nNews headlines Recent discussions highlight communication issues in financial decision-making among couples, particularly in high-stakes investments like real estate. This story reflects broader themes of risk tolerance and shared financial responsibilities.\\n\\n Recent discussions highlight communication issues in financial decision-making among couples, particularly in high-stakes investments like real estate. This story reflects broader themes of risk tolerance and shared financial responsibilities.\\n\\n Updated 17h ago · Powered by Yahoo Scout\\n View more\\nPrevious Close 61.72\\nOpen 61.48\\nBid 61.60 x 100\\nAsk 62.74 x 1400\\nDay's Range 60.75 - 63.39\\n52 Week Range 18.25 - 63.39\\nVolume 98,094,030\\nAvg. Volume 108,882,298\\nMarket Cap (intraday) 313.211B\\nBeta (5Y Monthly) 1.35\\nPE Ratio (TTM) --\\nEPS (TTM) -0.06\\nEarnings Date Apr 23, 2026\\nForward Dividend & Yield --\\nEx-Dividend Date Aug 7, 2024\\n1y Target Est 47.23\\n\\nIntel Corporation Overview Semiconductors / Technology\\n\\n Intel Corporation designs, develops, manufactures, markets, sells, and services computing and related end products and services in the United States, Ireland, Israel, and internationally. It operates through three segments: CCG, DCAI, and Intel Foundry. The company offers client computing group products, including client and commercial CPUs, discrete client GPUs, edge computing, and connectivity products; data center and AI products, such as server CPUs, discrete GPUs, and networking products; and semiconductors comprising wafer fabrication, substrates, and other related products and services. It also provides driving assistance and self-driving solutions; and develops and manufactures multi-beam mask writing tools. The company sells its products through sales organizations, distributors, resellers, retailers, and OEM partners. It serves original equipment manufacturers, original design manufacturers, cloud service providers, and other manufacturers and service providers. Intel Corporation has a strategic collaboration with Infosys Limited to develop a multi-layer AI fabric that unifies infrastructure, models, data, applications, and workflows into a composable and agent-ready ecosystem. The company was incorporated in 1968 and is headquartered in Santa Clara, California.\\n www.intel.com\\n 85,100\\n\\nFull Time Employees\\n\\nDecember 27\\n\\nFiscal Year Ends\\n\\nTechnology\\n\\nSector\\n\\nSemiconductors\\n\\nIndustry\\n\\n More about Intel Corporation\\n\\nRecent News: INTC\\n View More\\n All News Earnings Calls Press Releases SEC Filings\\n https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/stocks/articles/bull-vs-bear-meta-platforms-195000921.html Bull vs. Bear: Is Meta Platforms a Buy or Sell? Motley Fool 12m ago\\n\\n https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/options/articles/could-investing-10-000-leveraged-193300755.html Could Investing $10,000 in This Leveraged ETF Make You a Millionaire? Motley Fool 29m ago\\n\\n https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/stocks/articles/want-play-reshoring-theme-might-192100901.html Want to Play the Reshoring Theme? You Might Want to Buy These Stocks South of the Border. Motley Fool 41m ago\\n\\n https://finance.yahoo.com/sectors/technology/articles/dont-term-generational-buying-opportunity-184800726.html I Don't Use the Term \\\"Generational Buying Opportunity\\\" Lightly. Here's Why It Applies to This Beaten-Down Tech Stock. Motley Fool 1h ago\\n\\n https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/stocks/articles/wall-street-analysts-sell-stock-183300499.html Wall Street Analysts Say Sell on This Stock. Here's Why They're Wrong. Motley Fool 1