/7 Wall St. 8h ago\\n\\n https://finance.yahoo.com/m/7d38e948-9f51-338d-a4f3-3bd051df3872/us-iran-talks-end-with-no.html US-Iran Talks End With No Deal, Bitcoin Slumps in Potential Stock Market Preview Barrons.com 18h ago\\n\\n https://finance.yahoo.com/sectors/technology/articles/meta-unity-vr-deal-reshape-230755955.html Will Meta Unity VR Deal Reshape Unity Software's (U) Role in Immersive and AI-Powered Tools? Simply Wall St. 23h ago\\n\\n View More\\n\\nRelated Videos: META\\n\\n Meta stock is still 'dirt cheap' despite Muse Spark rally Meta (META) released artificial intelligence (AI) model Muse Spark on Wednesday, triggering a stock rally this week. Wedbush Securities managing director and global head of technology research Dan Ives chats with Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi about why he still sees Meta as a value stock. Yahoo Finance Video · 2d ago AMZN +2.02%\\n\\nMSFT -0.59%\\n02:42 Meta expands CoreWeave partnership with new $21B AI cloud deal Yahoo Finance Video 3d ago\\n03:45 Dow spikes by over 1,300, oil prices retreat in ceasefire rally Yahoo Finance Video 4d ago\\n00:56 Meta launches Muse Spark AI, BofA raises 2026 chip forecast to $1.3T Yahoo Finance Video 4d ago\\n\\nPerformance Overview: META\\n\\n Trailing total returns as of 4/10/2026, which may include dividends or other distributions. Benchmark is S&P 500 (^GSPC).\\n\\nYTD Return\\n\\n META\\n 4.50%\\n\\n S&P 500 (^GSPC)\\n 0.42%\\n\\n1-Year Return\\n\\n META\\n 15.66%\\n\\n S&P 500 (^GSPC)\\n 29.40%\\n\\n3-Year Return\\n\\n META\\n 195.60%\\n\\n S&P 500 (^GSPC)\\n 65.90%\\n\\n5-Year Return\\n\\n META\\n 103.16%\\n\\n S&P 500 (^GSPC)\\n 65.11%\\n\\nEarnings Trends: META\\n View More\\n\\nEarnings Per Share\\n gaap GAAP\\n nongaap Normalized\\n\\n gaap GAAP\\n nongaap Normalized\\n\\n /quote/META/analysis/\\n\\nRevenue vs. Earnings\\n yearly Annual\\n quarterly Quarterly\\n\\n yearly Annual\\n quarterly Quarterly\\n\\n Q4 FY25\\n\\n Revenue 59.89B\\n\\n Earnings 22.77B\\n\\n Q1\\nFY25